sa eva brahmādir ucyate.

<commentary>katham ity āha—brahmetyādi. yata eva suviśuddhabodharūpatvād asau buddhas tad eva paraṃ brahma. tasmāt sa eva brahmā. nirvṛttita iti mokṣarūpatvād ity arthaḥ. nirvṛtir nirvāṇaṃ mokṣo niḥśreyasaṃ buddha iti paryāyāḥ. viṣaṇād iti tādātmyena praveśāt. kva? paramagambhīre dharmakāye. viśateḥ ktapratyayaḥ ṣatvaṇatve ca. sadā sukalyāṇād iti dhruvakalyāṇatvāt paramakalyāṇatvāc ca. sarvar ityādi. yasmād asau sarveṣām ātmani dharmadhātau vedakatvena sthitaḥ, tasmāt sarvaḥ.</commentary>

satsukhatvenety anāsravadhruvottamasukhatvena. bodhanād rater iti tasyaiva niruttarasya sukhasya vedanād yo hi taṃ na vedayate, nidrāṇa evāsau. brahmāditvaṃ yad uddiṣṭaṃ tad iyatā nirdiṣṭam—deha ityādinā.
